{{see|الجزاير}}

==Arabic==
[[Category:Arabic nouns]]
===Etymology===
From Arabic {{ARchar|[[جزيرة]]}} (djazí:ra) "[[island]]", referring to several small islands that used to exist in the Bay of Algiers. Most of the islands are now connected to the shore or have been removed.

===Proper noun===
'''{{ARchar|الجَزَائِر}}''' (al-djazá:’ir) {{p}}

# [[Algiers]]
# [[Algeria]]
# the [[islands]]

